| **Existing PARIVESH Portal (Current Website)**                                | **PARIVESH 3.0 (Hackathon Problem Statement)**                                                                   |
| ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Single-window portal for **environment, forest, wildlife and CRZ clearances** | Focused **workflow-driven portal specifically for environmental clearance meeting workflow**                     |
| Allows **Project Proponent registration and application submission**          | Full **role-based workflow with strict RBAC (Admin, PP/RQP, Scrutiny Team, MoM Team)**                           |
| Tracks proposal status (submitted, processing, approved etc.)                 | **Linear workflow enforcement:** Draft → Submitted → Under Scrutiny → EDS → Referred → MoM Generated → Finalized |
| Provides **application submission and monitoring**                            | Complete **application lifecycle management including meeting documentation**                                    |
| Document uploads available for proposals                                      | **Automated document generation system** (Gist → Minutes of Meeting)                                             |
| Mostly **manual meeting preparation**                                         | **Auto-generation of Meeting Gist from application data**                                                        |
| Meeting minutes may be uploaded manually                                      | **System-generated MoM after editing the Gist**                                                                  |
| No clear internal workflow separation for teams                               | Dedicated dashboards for **Scrutiny Team and MoM Secretariat**                                                   |
| Users can track project proposals and clearance status                        | Teams can **verify documents, flag missing documents (EDS)**                                                     |
| Payment options exist but not fully modernized                                | **QR Code / UPI payment integration simulation**                                                                 |
| Limited template automation                                                   | **Admin-controlled master templates for Gist documents**                                                         |
| Information-heavy interface, difficult navigation                             | **Clean, modern UI/UX (Corporate blue/white)**                                                                   |
| Data visible but organization sometimes inconsistent                          | **Strict data isolation and role-based access security**                                                         |
| Focus mainly on **submission and approval process**                           | Focus on **decision-making workflow and meeting documentation process**                                          |
| Portal contains large database of project proposals and reports               | System designed as **CMS-based structured workflow system**                                                      |



